{"word":"οὐχί","slug":"οὐχί","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>οὐχί</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:οὐ\">οὐ</a></el> intensified]<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> in emphatic negative statement, <b>not <a href='B:500 13:10'>J 13:10f</a>; <a href='B:500 14:22'>14:22</a>; <a href='B:530 5:2'>1 Cor 5:2</a>; <a href='B:530 6:1'>6:1</a>; <a href='B:530 10:29'>10:29</a>;</b> with special force, <b>no <a href='B:490 1:60'>Lk 1:60</a>; <a href='B:490 12:51'>12:51</a>; <a href='B:490 16:30'>16:30</a>; <a href='B:500 9:9'>J 9:9</a></b> (‘no way’); <b><a href='B:520 3:27'>Ro 3:27</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ freq.\">freq.</a> in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ qu.\">qu.</a> with a tone suggesting that a positive answer ought to be self-evident or is a no-brainer, <b>not <a href='B:470 5:46'>Mt 5:46f</a>; <a href='B:470 6:25'>6:25</a>; <a href='B:470 12:11'>12:11</a>; <a href='B:490 17:8'>Lk 17:8</a></b> (<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἀλλά\">ἀλλά</a></el> not rather), <b>17; 24:26; <a href='B:500 7:42'>J 7:42</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a>; <a href='B:510 5:4'>Ac 5:4</a>; <a href='B:510 7:50'>7:50</a>; <a href='B:520 8:32'>Ro 8:32</a>; <a href='B:530 3:3'>1 Cor 3:3</a>; <a href='B:530 10:16'>10:16</a>; <a href='B:590 2:19'>1 Th 2:19</a>; <a href='B:650 1:14'>Hb 1:14</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:οὐχ\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ὀφειλέτης\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}